"{\"uid\": \"canberratimes.com.au-story-8629528-olympic-heros-bravery-award-for-ice-cool-surf-rescue\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited news content and The Canberra Times app.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Canberra Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Premium subscribers also enjoy interactive puzzles and access to the digital version of our print edition - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The term \\\"doing a Bradbury\\\" has taken on a whole new meaning.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 292, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  Steven Bradbury became synonymous with unexpected success after a shock 2002 Winter Olympic victory.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999997853593, \"rank\": 2.1448559261121532e-10, \"text\": \"Steven Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q847400\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Bradbury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now the former speed skater is being hailed for his bravery after saving four girls in Queensland's Sunshine Coast surf.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"score\": 0.9999271489612932, \"rank\": 6.859169812258494e-05, \"text\": \"Queensland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Bradbury was the last man standing in the men's 1000m short track final at Salt Lake City, winning Australia's first Winter Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}, {\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.8449607239820853, \"rank\": 0.18348696172121953, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}, {\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999631081671, \"rank\": 2.14579555253614e-08, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twenty years later, he went into \\\"Olympic mode\\\" again to rescue four teenagers from rough seas at Caloundra.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6546860330456592e-24, \"text\": \"Caloundra\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His March 2022 heroics have officially been recognised after receiving a commendation for brave conduct from the Queensland governor in Brisbane.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Queensland governor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999997584214108, \"rank\": 2.412839657417677e-07, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With the Olympic gold, I had been training my guts out for 14 years to get myself in that position,\\\" Mr Bradbury told AAP.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not sure how you compare it with a bravery award.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it was nice to know that the body and the mind could switch back to Olympic mode for a few minutes when required.\\\"\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Bradbury was teaching his son how to surf in 2022 when he saw what he thought was a log in the huge swell.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then I realised it was a human head,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I clicked straight into gear.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I sent my son to the lifeguards and paddled out.\\\"\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Bradbury first came across a 12-year-old girl.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1544, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had never seen anyone look so scared before in my life,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After that I saw three more heads further out.\\\"\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He took the 12-year-old to shore before paddling out to the others.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One was hyperventilating and one was panicking.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were just getting pounded wave after wave,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got all three on the board but we had no momentum.\\\"\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Suddenly the lifeguard his son had alerted arrived, plucking two girls from the water.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Bradbury took the other to shore before all three teens got the medical all clear.\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2036, \"end\": 2044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The girl I got out of the water first came running up to me on the beach afterwards and hugged me, she said 'thank you for saving my life',\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was when it sort of dawned on me I had done something pretty cool.\\\"\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Bradbury received his bravery award from Queensland Governor Jeannette Young on Tuesday, earning Australian Olympic Committee praise.\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2350, \"end\": 2358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}, {\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Queensland Governor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Governor_of_Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 2411, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeannette_Young\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeannette Young\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeannette_Young\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeannette_Young\"}, {\"begin\": 2447, \"end\": 2475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have always admired Steven for the way he has made history on the ice but his actions ... reflect an incredible achievement - saving four young lives,\\\" AOC president Ian Chesterman said.\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3775476673304488e-12, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2655, \"end\": 2669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Chesterman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ian Chesterman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Chesterman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Chesterman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He always had amazing courage as an athlete and it has served him well here.\\\"\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Bradbury may have won historic gold but the four-time Olympian rated the 2022 rescue \\\"one of the greatest days of my life\\\".\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2760, \"end\": 2768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"score\": 0.9999999926990313, \"rank\": 7.301131664983202e-09, \"text\": \"Bradbury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Bradbury\"}, {\"begin\": 2814, \"end\": 2822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999322426, \"rank\": 2.7638476059343023e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not feel like a bravery award is necessary but I am happy to accept it and feel pretty proud about it,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 3003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The feeling of knowing that you have saved people's lives is something I will take to my grave.\\\"\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Associated Press  Daily  Today's top stories curated by our news team.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also includes evening update.\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As it happens  Do not miss updates on news about the Public Service.\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Grab a quick bite of today's latest news from around the region and the nation.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Catch up on the news of the day and unwind with great reading for your evening.\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  Get the editor's insights: what's happening & why it matters.\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Twice weekly  Stay in the know on news that matters to you with twice weekly newsletters from The Senior.\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 